Our Solution: PayFlow is an AI-powered invoicing platform that predicts payment likelihood and automatically triggers personalized follow-up sequences. Unlike generic invoicing tools, we use behavioral signals to optimize timing and messaging.

The Market: The $12B invoicing software market is growing 15% annually. We're targeting the 30M US small businesses, starting with professional services firms.

Business Model: SaaS subscription at $49/month for small businesses, $199/month for agencies. 78% gross margin.

Traction: 2,400 paying customers, $140K MRR, growing 18% month-over-month.

Team: CEO Jane Smith spent 10 years at Square. CTO John Doe built fraud detection at Stripe.

Vision: We're building the financial nervous system for small business.
